The positive CD has the following updated information: Lush, cinematic 1970s progressive/pop production: sweeping strings, inventive orchestration, choir‑like multi‑tracked vocals, ambitious layering and dramatic dynamic shifts. Meticulous studio craft and clear mastering prioritize transparency within density — ideal for listeners who enjoy studio spectacle that heightens emotion and melody.

